{
  "page": "Blood & Fire",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For the fictional book, see <a href=\"/index.php/Blood_and_Fire\" title=\"Blood and Fire\">Blood and Fire</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #DEDEE2; text-align:center; font-style: italic;\">Blood &amp; Fire</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Author</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/George_R._R._Martin\" title=\"George R. R. Martin\">George R. R. Martin</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Country</th><td>\n<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/United_States\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:United States\">United States</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Language</th><td>\n<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/English_language\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:English language\">English</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Series</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire\">A Song of Ice and Fire</a></i></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Genre(s)</th><td>\n<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fantasy\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Fantasy\">Fantasy</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Preceded&#160;by</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><i><b>Blood &amp; Fire</b></i><sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> is the planned title of the sequel of <i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, written by <a href=\"/index.php/George_R.R._Martin\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"George R.R. Martin\">George R.R. Martin</a>. It will cover the history of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">House Targaryen</a> from the reign of <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_III_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon III Targaryen\">Aegon III</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Robert%27s_Rebellion\" title=\"Robert&#39;s Rebellion\">Robert's Rebellion</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>By September 2024, Martin had written \"some new pages\" of <i>Blood &amp; Fire</i>, working on it alongside <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Blood_%26_Fire&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">George R.R. Martin (July 11, 2024). <a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://georgerrmartin.com/notablog/2024/07/11/here-there-be-dragons-2/\">Here There Be Dragons</a>. Not A Blog. Retrieved July 13, 2024.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">George R.R. Martin (July 22, 2017). <a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://georgerrmartin.com/notablog/2017/07/22/the-swords-are-drawn/\">The Swords Are Drawn</a>. Not A Blog. Retrieved July 13, 2024.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">George R.R. Martin (9 September 2024) <a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://georgerrmartin.com/notablog/2024/09/09/a-belated-blog/\">A Belated Blog</a>. Not A Blog. Retrieved 9 September 2024</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;padding-top:3px;text-align:left;width:6.8em;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template:GRRM_works\" title=\"Template:GRRM works\"><span title=\"View this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">v</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/index.php?title=Template_talk:GRRM_works&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Template talk:GRRM works (page does not exist)\"><span title=\"Discuss this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">d</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-edit\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php?title=Template:GRRM_works&amp;action=edit\"><span title=\"Edit this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">e</span></a></li></ul></div><div class=\"\" style=\"font-size:110%;\">\nWorks by <a href=\"/index.php/George_R._R._Martin\" title=\"George R. R. Martin\">George R. R. Martin</a> in the world of <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire\">A Song of Ice and Fire</a></i></div></th></tr><tr style=\"height:2px;\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\">Novels</td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"pad